name: AWS - GuardDuty - Extension
description:
The 'AWS - GuardDuty - Extension' pack provides supports for aws-gd-*-members commands.
The current pack includes commands,
1. aws-gd-list-members (Describes Amazon GuardDuty members for the specified detector ID)
2. aws-gd-get-members (Describes Amazon GuardDuty members for the specified detector ID & account ID)
author: Sayan Ghosh
